      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert n8n workflow troubleshooting assistant.\n\nAnalyze the following workflow error:{{ $json.Error }}\n\n\n\nBased on this error, provide a detailed analysis in the following format:\n\n1. Error Summary\n- Explain in simple language what the error means.\n\n2. Root Cause\n- Identify the most likely cause(s) of the error.\n- Mention any assumptions if the exact cause cannot be determined.\n\n3. Recommended Solution\n- Provide step-by-step instructions to resolve the issue.\n- If there are multiple possible fixes, rank them from most likely to least likely.\n\n4. Priority Level\nClassify this issue as one of:\n- High: The workflow has completely failed, data loss may occur, critical integrations are down, or manual intervention is immediately required.\n- Medium: The workflow is partially working, affects some users or records, or may become critical if not addressed.\n- Low: Minor issue, warning, cosmetic problem, or temporary issue with minimal business impact.\n\nExplain why you assigned this priority.\n\n5. Prevention\nRecommend best practices to prevent this error from occurring again.\n\n6. Confidence Level\nIndicate your confidence in the diagnosis as High, Medium, or Low, and explain why.\n\nKeep the response concise but actionable.",
        "needsFallback": true,
        "options": {}
      },
