      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a formatting assistant.\n\nTake the provided {{ $json.output }} and reorganize it into the following sections. Do not change the meaning of the content, add new information, or remove important details. Simply classify the information into the appropriate headings.\n\nUse the exact headings below and output them in this order:\n\n## Error Summary\nProvide a concise summary of the error or issue.\n\n## Root Cause\nState the underlying cause(s) of the error.\n\n## Recommended Solution\nList the recommended steps to resolve the issue. If there are multiple solutions, present them as bullet points.\n\n## Priority Level\nAssign one of the following values:\n- Critical\n- High\n- Medium\n- Low\n\nInclude a brief justification for the selected priority.\n\n## Prevention\nDescribe actions or best practices that would help prevent this error from occurring again.\n\n## Confidence Level\nState one of the following:\n- High\n- Medium\n- Low\n\nInclude a one-sentence explanation of why this confidence level was assigned.\n\nRules:\n- Preserve all important information from the original output.\n- Do not invent facts or assumptions.\n- If information for a section is missing, write \"Not provided.\"\n- Return only the formatted output using the headings above.\n- Ensure the output is clear, professional, and easy to read.\n-Every section should go to the next node as a separate JSON object that can be dragged.\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "needsFallback": true,
        "options": {}
